---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="App & SaaS Development — Federica Fanì"
  description="Sviluppo app Android native in Flutter, web app e piccoli SaaS. Dal concept al deploy, con approccio artigianale."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="app-hero">
    <div class="app-hero-inner">
      <div class="breadcrumb reveal">
        <a href="/servizi">Servizi</a>
        <span>→</span>
        <span>App & SaaS Development</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">App & SaaS<br><em>Development</em></h1>
      <p class="app-hero-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">
        Dal concept al deploy. Niente soluzioni preconfezionate, ogni progetto pensato da zero.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- APPROCCIO -->
  <section class="section approach-section">
    <div class="approach-grid">
      <div class="approach-text">
        <span class="eyebrow reveal">Il mio approccio</span>
        <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Artigianale, non industriale</h2>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2">Sviluppo app Android native in Flutter e web app, dal concept al deploy. Lavoro su progetti propri e accetto collaborazioni freelance con un approccio artigianale: niente soluzioni preconfezionate, ogni progetto viene pensato da zero in base alle esigenze reali.</p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="margin-top: 12px;">Sono aperta a progetti proporzionati a un lavoro individuale: app Android, web app, piccoli SaaS. Se hai un'idea e vuoi capire se è realizzabile, scrivimi.</p>

        <div class="tech-stack reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="tech-label">Stack tecnologico</div>
          <div class="tech-pills">
            <span class="tech-pill">Flutter</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Dart</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Firebase</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Android</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Astro</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">HTML/CSS/JS</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">GitHub</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Vercel</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="approach-side reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="approach-stat">
          <div class="stat-big">Flutter</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Framework principale · usato da Google Pay, BMW, Nubank</div>
        </div>
        <div class="approach-stat">
          <div class="stat-big">Android</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Target primario · iOS su richiesta</div>
        </div>
        <div class="approach-stat">
          <div class="stat-big">1 persona</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Nessun intermediario, contatto diretto</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROGETTI -->
  <div class="section-dark">
    <section class="section projects-section">
      <div class="sec-header">
        <div class="sec-header-left">
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light reveal">Portfolio</span>
          <h2 class="sec-title-light reveal reveal-delay-1">Progetti realizzati</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/portfolio" class="sec-link sec-link-light reveal">Vedi tutto →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="projects-grid">
        <div class="project-card reveal">
          <div class="project-header">
            <div class="project-ico">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="project-tag">Android · Flutter</div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-name">Magnebevo Client App</div>
          <div class="project-desc">App Android per i clienti del locale Magnebevo (Pigneto, Roma). Menu, eventi, promozioni e aggiornamenti in tempo reale.</div>
          <div class="project-client">Cliente: Magnebevo · Via del Pigneto 93, Roma</div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="project-header">
            <div class="project-ico">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="project-tag">Android · Flutter</div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-name">Magnebevo Staff App</div>
          <div class="project-desc">App Android per la gestione interna dello staff. Strumento operativo per semplificare comunicazione e organizzazione quotidiana del team.</div>
          <div class="project-client">Cliente: Magnebevo · Uso interno</div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card project-card-soon reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="project-header">
            <div class="project-ico">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="project-tag">In sviluppo</div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-name">Altri progetti</div>
          <div class="project-desc">Progetti SaaS in sviluppo. I dettagli saranno disponibili al lancio.</div>
          <div class="project-soon">Prossimamente</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- PREZZI -->
  <section class="section pricing-section">
    <div class="sec-header">
      <div class="sec-header-left">
        <span class="eyebrow reveal">Investimento</span>
        <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Tariffe sviluppo</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="pricing-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">Ogni progetto è diverso — questi sono punti di riferimento. Il preventivo finale dipende dalla complessità e dalle funzionalità richieste.</p>

    <div class="dev-pricing-grid">
      <div class="dev-pricing-card reveal">
        <div class="dev-pricing-header">
          <div class="dev-p-label">Consulenza</div>
          <div class="dev-p-price">€50<span>/ora</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="dev-p-desc">Analisi del progetto, definizione requisiti, revisione codice esistente, supporto tecnico.</div>
        <ul class="dev-features">
          <li>Analisi fattibilità tecnica</li>
          <li>Definizione architettura</li>
          <li>Revisione e ottimizzazione codice</li>
          <li>Supporto post-lancio</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="dev-pricing-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="dev-pricing-header">
          <div class="dev-p-label">App MVP</div>
          <div class="dev-p-price">da €3.000</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dev-p-desc">App Android funzionale con le funzionalità essenziali. Ideale per validare un'idea prima di investire di più.</div>
        <ul class="dev-features">
          <li>App Android in Flutter</li>
          <li>3–5 schermate principali</li>
          <li>Firebase backend base</li>
          <li>Deploy su Play Store</li>
          <li>1 mese di supporto post-lancio</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="dev-pricing-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="dev-pricing-header">
          <div class="dev-p-label">App completa</div>
          <div class="dev-p-price">preventivo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dev-p-desc">App con funzionalità avanzate, autenticazione utenti, database, notifiche push e pannello admin.</div>
        <ul class="dev-features">
          <li>App Android completa in Flutter</li>
          <li>Autenticazione e profili utente</li>
          <li>Database e backend Firebase</li>
          <li>Notifiche push</li>
          <li>Pannello admin web</li>
          <li>3 mesi di supporto post-lancio</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="dev-p-note">Preventivo personalizzato su richiesta</div>
      </div>

      <div class="dev-pricing-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="dev-pricing-header">
          <div class="dev-p-label">Sito web / Web app</div>
          <div class="dev-p-price">da €800</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dev-p-desc">Siti statici, landing page, portfolio o web app semplici. Stack: Astro, HTML/CSS/JS, Vercel.</div>
        <ul class="dev-features">
          <li>Design personalizzato</li>
          <li>Mobile responsive</li>
          <li>SEO ottimizzato</li>
          <li>Deploy e configurazione dominio</li>
          <li>CMS opzionale</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-disclaimer reveal">
      Tutti i prezzi sono IVA esclusa e indicativi. Il preventivo finale viene definito dopo un'analisi del progetto. I tempi di consegna variano in base alla complessità.
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="section-dark">
    <section class="section cta-section">
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light reveal">Parliamo</span>
        <h2 class="sec-title-light reveal reveal-delay-1">Hai un'idea?</h2>
        <p class="cta-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">Scrivimi per capire insieme se il tuo progetto è fattibile, quanto costa e quanto tempo ci vuole. La prima analisi è gratuita.</p>
        <div class="cta-btns reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <a href="/contatti" class="btn btn-gold">Scrivimi</a>
          <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn-outline-light">Guarda il portfolio</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

</Layout>

<style>
.app-hero {
  padding: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px) clamp(32px, 4vw, 56px);
  background: var(--blue-pale);
}

.app-hero-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }

.breadcrumb {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--blue-mid);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.breadcrumb a { color: var(--blue); transition: opacity 0.2s; }
.breadcrumb a:hover { opacity: 0.7; }

.app-hero h1 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--blue-dark);
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.app-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--blue); }

.app-hero-sub {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--blue-mid);
  font-style: italic;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
}

/* APPROACH */
.approach-section { padding-top: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); padding-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); }

.approach-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
  gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
  align-items: start;
}

.approach-text h2 { color: var(--blue-dark); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.approach-text p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--blue-mid); line-height: 1.8; }

.tech-stack { margin-top: 28px; }

.tech-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--blue);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.tech-pills { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }

.tech-pill {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 5px 12px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  background: var(--blue-light);
  color: var(--blue);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(43,79,216,0.2);
}

.approach-side { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }

.approach-stat {
  padding: 18px 20px;
  background: var(--blue-light);
  border-radius: var(--r-md);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(43,79,216,0.15);
}

.stat-big {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--blue);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.stat-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--blue-mid); line-height: 1.5; }

/* PROJECTS */
.projects-section { padding-top: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); padding-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); }

.projects-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
}

.project-card {
  background: rgba(43,79,216,0.1);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(123,167,232,0.2);
  border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  padding: 24px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}

.project-card-soon { opacity: 0.6; }

.project-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
}

.project-ico {
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  border-radius: var(--r-sm);
  background: rgba(43,79,216,0.25);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: var(--azure);
}

.project-tag {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  background: rgba(43,79,216,0.2);
  color: var(--azure);
  padding: 3px 9px;
  border-radius: 20px;
}

.project-name {
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--white);
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
}

.project-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--azure); line-height: 1.7; flex: 1; }

.project-client {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(123,167,232,0.5);
  font-style: italic;
}

.project-soon {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* PRICING */
.pricing-section { padding-top: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); padding-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); }

.pricing-sub {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--blue-mid);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  font-style: italic;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  max-width: 600px;
}

.dev-pricing-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 14px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.dev-pricing-card {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(43,79,216,0.12);
  border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  padding: 24px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 14px;
}

.dev-pricing-header { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }

.dev-p-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--blue);
}

.dev-p-price {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 32px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--blue-dark);
  line-height: 1;
}

.dev-p-price span { font-size: 16px; color: var(--blue-mid); }

.dev-p-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--blue-mid); line-height: 1.6; }

.dev-features {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 7px;
  flex: 1;
}

.dev-features li {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--blue-mid);
  padding-left: 14px;
  position: relative;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.dev-features li::before {
  content: '→';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--blue);
  font-size: 11px;
}

.dev-p-note {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--blue);
  font-style: italic;
  margin-top: auto;
}

.pricing-disclaimer {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--blue-mid);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* CTA */
.cta-section { text-align: center; }
.cta-section .eyebrow { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.cta-section h2 { margin-bottom: 16px; }
.cta-sub { font-size: 15px; color: var(--azure); max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 32px; line-height: 1.75; }
.cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .dev-pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .projects-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 480px; }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .approach-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .dev-pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
